Island War Unblocked Game is a Chrome extension that allows you to play the popular offline game Island War even when it is blocked by your school or workplace. The extension works by bypassing the block and allowing you to access the game directly in your browser popup.

Allows you to play Island War even when it is blocked by your school or workplace.
Works with any web browser that supports Chrome extensions.
Free to use and does not require any downloads or installations.
Easy to install and use.
